      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-properties-card col-md-4">
      <div class="well">
        <%= link_to "Ash Grove", ash_grove_path, class:"h3 text-center" %>
        <p>6 Bed</p>
         <%= link_to image_tag("http://idswebhost.co.uk/guildford/images/23ashg/outside1.jpg"), ash_grove_path %>
        <p>Our Ash Grove house is just a 3 minute walk from Guildford uni! It's 
        recently rennovated with 6 light, airy bedrooms and off-street parking for 5 cars.</p>
        <p class="uni-walk"><i class="fa fa-university"></i> 3 mins walk from uni</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-properties-card col-md-4">
